quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  27,15,"Dájúdájú A fún (Ànábì) Dāwūd àti (Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n ní ìmọ̀. Àwọn méjèèjì sì sọ pé: \"Ọpẹ́ ni fún Allāhu, Ẹni tí Ó fún wa ní oore àjùlọ lórí ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Rẹ̀, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  27,16,"(Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n sì jogún (Ànábì) Dāwūd. Ó sọ pé: \"Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn, Wọ́n fi ohùn ẹyẹ mọ̀ wá. Wọ́n sì fún wa ní gbogbo n̄ǹkan. Dájúdájú èyí, òhun ni oore àjùlọ pọ́nńbélé"
  27,17,"A sì kó jọ fún (Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n, àwọn ọmọ ogun rẹ̀ nínú àlùjànnú, ènìyàn àti ẹyẹ. A sì ń kó wọn jọ papọ̀ mọ́ra wọn"
  27,18,"títí wọ́n fi dé àfonífojì àwọn àwúrèbe. Àwúrèbe kan sì wí pé: \"Ẹ̀yin àwúrèbe, ẹ wọ inú ilé yín lọ, kí (Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n àti àwọn ọmọ ogun rẹ̀ má baà tẹ̀ yín rẹ́ mọ́lẹ̀. Wọn kò sì níí fura"
  27,19,"Nígbà náà, (Ànábì Sulaemọ̄n) rẹ́rìn-ín músẹ́, ẹ̀rín pa á nítorí ọ̀rọ̀ (àwúrèbe náà). Ó sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, fi mọ̀ mí bí mo ṣe máa dúpẹ́ ìdẹ̀ra Rẹ, èyí tí O fi ṣe ìdẹ̀ra fún èmi àti àwọn òbí mi méjèèjì. (Fi mọ̀ mí) bí mo ṣe máa ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, èyí tí O yọ́nú sí. Pẹ̀lú àánú Rẹ fi mí sáààrin àwọn ẹrúsìn Rẹ, àwọn ẹni rere.”"
  27,20,"Ó ṣàbẹ̀wò àwọn ẹyẹ, ó sì sọ pé: “Nítorí kí ni mi ò ṣe rí ẹyẹ hudhuda? Àbí ó jẹ́ ọ̀kan nínú àwọn tí kò wá ni"
  27,21,"Dájúdájú mo máa jẹ ẹ́ níyà líle, tàbí kí n̄g dúńbú rẹ̀, tàbí kí ó mú ẹ̀rí t’ó yanjú wá fún mi.”"
  27,22,"(Ànábì Sulaemọ̄n) kò dúró pẹ́ (títí ó fi dé), ó sì wí pé: \"Mo mọ n̄ǹkan tí o ò mọ̀. Mo sì mú ìró kan t’ó dájú wá bá ọ láti ìlú Saba’i"
  27,23,"Dájúdájú èmi bá obìnrin kan (níbẹ̀), t’ó ń ṣe ìjọba lé wọn lórí. Wọ́n fún un ní gbogbo n̄ǹkan. Ó sì ní ìtẹ́ ńlá kan"
  27,24,"Mo sì bá òun àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ tí wọ́n ń forí kanlẹ̀ fún òòrùn lẹ́yìn Allāhu. Èṣù sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ wọn ní ọ̀ṣọ́ fún wọn. Ó ṣẹ́rí wọn kúrò lójú ọ̀nà (òdodo). Nítorí náà, wọn kò sì mọ̀nà"
  27,25,"láti forí kanlẹ̀ fún Allāhu, Ẹni t’Ó ń mú ọrọ̀ t’ó pamọ́ sínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ jáde, Ó sì mọ ohun tí ẹ̀ ń fi pamọ́ àti ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣàfi hàn"
  27,26,"Allāhu, kò sí ọlọ́hun tí ìjọ́sìn tọ́ sí àfi Òun, Olúwa Ìtẹ́ ńlá"
  27,27,"Ó sọ pé: \"A máa wòye bóyá òdodo l’o sọ ni tàbí o wà nínú àwọn òpùrọ́"
  27,28,"Mú ìwé mi yìí lọ, kí o jù ú sí wọn. Lẹ́yìn náà, kí o takété sí wọn, kí o sì wo ohun tí wọn yóò dá padà (ní èsì)"
  27,29,"(Bilƙīs) sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjòyè, dájúdájú wọ́n ti ju ìwé alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé kan sí mi"
  27,30,"Dájúdájú ó wá láti ọ̀dọ̀ (Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n. Dájúdájú ó (sọ pé) “Ní orúkọ Allāhu, Àjọkẹ́-ayé, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  27,31,"Kí ẹ má ṣègbéraga sí mi, kí ẹ sì wá sí ọ̀dọ̀ mi (láti di) mùsùlùmí.”"